Use the standard library
This is how to is_simple_power of x and n:
  When x is 1, then:
    The answer is 1
  End when
  Remember that current is x
  Do this x times:
    When remainder of current and n is not 0, then:
      The answer is 0
    End when
    Remember that current is quotient of current and n
    When current is 1, then:
      The answer is 1
    End when
  End do
  The answer is 0
